Ext.data.JsonP['Adding_PHP,_Ruby_or_Python_Support']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Adding PHP, Ruby or Python Support</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-37525491\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Adding PHP, Ruby or Python Support</h1>\n    <p>As of Studio Release 3.1.0, support for server-side languages is optional to slim down the Studio installer. To add them back in again:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Launch Studio    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Go to <strong class=\" \">Help</strong> &gt; <strong class=\" \">Install New Software&#x2026;</strong>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Enter the following URL in the <strong class=\" \">Work with:</strong> field:    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">PHP</strong> - <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"http://download.appcelerator.com/aptana/studio3/php/update/stable\" target=\"_blank\">http://download.appcelerator.com/aptana/studio3/php/update/stable</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Ruby</strong> - <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"http://download.appcelerator.com/aptana/studio3/ruby/update/stable\" target=\"_blank\">http://download.appcelerator.com/aptana/studio3/ruby/update/stable</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Pydev</strong> - <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"http://download.appcelerator.com/aptana/studio3/pydev/update/stable\" target=\"_blank\">http://download.appcelerator.com/aptana/studio3/pydev/update/stable</a>    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p>Check the top level node in the table and go through the wizard to install.    </p>\n</li></ol>        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=37525491\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Adding PHP, Ruby or Python Support"});